---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use - My Little Pillow">
  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">My Little Pillow Store</a></div>
  <main>
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to the whimsical world of <strong>My Little Pillow</strong>!
      Before you embark on this lighthearted journey, please take a moment to
      read our Terms of Use. By accessing our site, you agree to embrace the
      humor, wit, and playful spirit of <strong>My Little Pillow</strong>. If
      you’re ready to chuckle and not take things too seriously, read on!
    </p>

    <h2>1. Sense of Humor Required</h2>
    <p>
      Our site is designed for individuals who appreciate a good laugh. If
      you’re prone to getting your feelings hurt, this might not be the place
      for you. We highly recommend having a well-developed funny bone before
      proceeding.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Party-Ready Attitude</h2>
    <p>
      Visitors to our site should be the kind of people others want to invite to
      their parties. Leave the seriousness at the door, please.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Lighthearted Content</h2>
    <p>
      The content on this site is intended for entertainment purposes only. Our
      (non-existent) product, <strong>My Little Pillow</strong>, is all about
      adding a touch of humor to your day. If you find yourself laughing out
      loud, we’ve done our job.
    </p>

    <h2>4. No Offense Zone</h2>
    <p>
      We strive to keep things light and breezy. If something tickles you the
      wrong way, remember it’s all in good fun. Life’s too short to be serious
      all the time, so let’s keep the vibes positive and the laughs rolling.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Share the Joy</h2>
    <p>
      Feel free to share our content with friends, family, and anyone else who
      could use a good laugh. Just remember to spread the joy responsibly.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Feedback Welcome</h2>
    <p>
      We love hearing from our visitors! If you have suggestions, funny
      anecdotes, or just want to say hi, drop us a line. We’re always looking to
      improve and make you laugh even harder.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Respect the Fun</h2>
    <p>
      While we’re all about fun and games, we do ask that you respect our site
      and fellow visitors. Any form of harassment, negativity, or unkind
      behavior will not be tolerated.
    </p>

    <p>
      By using this site, you acknowledge that you are here for a good time and
      agree to our whimsical terms. Now, go ahead and explore <a href="/"
        ><strong>My Little Pillow</strong></a
      >—your dose of daily delight!
    </p>

    <p>Enjoy and keep smiling!</p>

    <p><strong>My Little Pillow Team</strong></p>

    <p><a href="/">Back to My Little Pillow Store home page</a></p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .breadcrumb {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.25rem;
    left: 1rem;
    font-size: var(--step-1);
  }
  h1 {
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }
  h2 {
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
</style>
